==Description== 

The [[Image:Fasteners_Simplify.svg|24px]] '''Fasteners Simplify''' command creates non-parametric copies of fasteners. This can be useful if you want to share a document containing fasteners with users who do not have the [[Fasteners_Workbench|Fasteners Workbench]] installed.

==Usage== 

# Select one or more fasteners.
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Fasteners_Simplify.svg|16px]] [[Fasteners_Simplify|Simplify shape]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Fasteners → [[Image:Fasteners_Simplify.svg|16px]] Simplify shape}} option from the menu.
# For each fastener a simplified copy is created.
# The {{PropertyView|Visibility}} property of the original fasteners is set to {{FALSE}}.
# Optionally delete the original fasteners.


